text: Inês Teixeira Pereira (born 26 May 1999) is a Portuguese footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Sporting CP. She has appeared for the Portugal women's national team. ==Career== Pereira has been capped for the Portugal national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * * Inês Pereira at Portuguese Football Federation (FPF) * Inês Pereira at Sporting CP Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese women's footballers Category:Portugal women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Campeonato Nacional de Futebol Feminino players Category:Sporting CP (women) footballers
